.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: metal, indie, house, soul, rock
The people have 5 different hobbies: woodworking, reading, rock-climbing, singing, skydiving
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: animation, adventure, mystery, superhero, comedy
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, roller, train, tram, bike
City: prague, hamburg, venice, san-francisco, berlin

1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the fan of metal
2. the person who's hobby is reading is the person traveling to prague
3. the person driving the skateboard is the fan of indie
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person driving the roller
5. the fan of indie is to the right of the fan of house
6. the person watching animation movies is the person traveling to berlin
7. the person watching adventure movies is the fan of soul
8. the person driving the train is in the middle
9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left
10. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg
11. the person watching adventure movies is to the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco
12. the person watching superhero movies is the person driving the tram
13. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person watching comedy movies
14. the person who's hobby is singing is to the left or right of the fan of rock

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Hobby	|   singing	|    rock-climbing	|     woodworking	|    reading	|    skydiving	|
| Music-Genre		|    soul	|      rock	|      metal	|     house	|     indie	|
| Transport	|     bike	|      roller	|      train	| tram	|     skateboard	|
| Movie-Genre		|     adventure	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| superhero	|   parliament	|
| City		|     hamburg	|     san-francisco	|     berlin	|     prague	|     venice	|
